    features: { title: "Key Features", content: "<ul><li><strong>9+ Case Formats</strong>: UPPERCASE, lowercase, Title Case, Sentence case, camelCase, PascalCase, snake_case, kebab-case, CONSTANT_CASE</li><li><strong>Instant Conversion</strong>: Results appear immediately when you click a format</li><li><strong>Multi-Line Support</strong>: Convert multiple lines of text at once</li><li><strong>Smart Parsing</strong>: Correctly splits words from camelCase, snake_case, or other formats</li><li><strong>One-Click Copy</strong>: Copy converted text to clipboard</li><li><strong>Batch Processing</strong>: Process multiple lines simultaneously</li></ul>" },
